{"tid":1383431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］730行動代號：山竹殺到黎 • 返工3.0","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:37:03.000Z","uid":69419,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a6331e03acd661e79f6a40b03ef22144c892c506","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得，山竹勁到點？      <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180919/s00046/4b992b8eb15dff0284add6bae5bd6846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180919%2Fs00046%2F4b992b8eb15dff0284add6bae5bd6846.jpg&h=3716339e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]blob:<a href=\"https://web.whatsapp.com/469b7012-305a-4c72-87a7-de21abce5829[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.whatsapp.com%2F469b7012-305a-4c72-87a7-de21abce5829%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=f4dbd44b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.whatsapp.com/469b7012-305a-4c72-87a7-de21abce5829[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n大交合路徑預測：730罷工風起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezULJ5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezULJ5x.jpg&h=376a71db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次罷工係呢場運動既契機。<br />\n<br />\n但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人一直好鍾意番工</span></strong>，要場颱風吹得夠耐，相信大家都無乜信心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而罷工一兩日，唔好話吹冧香港個市，可能連一條草都吹唔起</span></strong>。點先可以令到一啲堅定而又有條件罷工既手足，有理有據咁做，而又幫到啲想罷工但真係無條件既手足，令到佢地可以大條道理番唔到工！最緊要係，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">連奶共狗都因為咁而番唔撚到工。</span></span>不如，大家學下山竹，令到香港可以吹得起罷工風。  首先，地鐵有制禁：  大家係配合車長罷工都已經好多意見，以下有幾個po不妨參考： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375417/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375417/page/1</a>  <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382092/page/1?post=2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382092/page/1?post=2</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聲援地鐵車長</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n夢見每一個站有<span style=\"color: red;\">5-6個手足組隊</span>，一個站夠人，手足就會自動坐去下個站繼續，做呢個崗位既手足要<span style=\"color: red;\">不停換站，方可預防瘋狗症</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">重點係，轉車站唔知點解特別多人。  </span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">隧道啲收費集口</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n我夢入面，全香港只有幾條主要隧道，塞下塞下都會過到。但如果你出唔到去，敵人就入唔黎，就係做咗一個好有用既掩護。<br />\n大部分隧道每邊都得2-3條行車線，平排前後大約每條有5-7架車，相信效果會相當不錯。但只塞行車線可能好快有狗到，趕到你出隧道，<span style=\"color: green;\">所以收費閘口都係一個關鍵</span>，例如將軍澳隧道，每部車過都係3蚊，如果你用張<span style=\"color: green;\">1000蚊比佢慢慢找</span>，而每個閘口都有人咁做。再加上秀茂坪成日有車禍，咁樣，你係可以成功癱瘓成個將軍澳既居民。  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">番唔到工，咪home office?</span> </span></ins></strong><br />\nIT超合作運動： 利申本行唔係IT狗，但同為打工狗，深感outlook / gmail既重要性，IT狗一定要緊記<span style=\"color: blue;\">好好保護公司既Corp account assess right</span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">千祈唔好比server條電線鬆</span>。另外，提提大家，如果藍絲老闆用任何翻版軟件，尤其是mircosoft，記得打去比海關（熱線 2545 6182)，<span style=\"color: blue;\">參與反盜版獎賞計劃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n海關通常會係一兩日內朝早上公司巡查收電腦，電腦都被人收埋，廢青無奈響應罷工。大家一齊盡良好市民責任，<span style=\"color: blue;\">保護知識產權，進行超合作運動！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins>頻率</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n學下法國：鐵路工會表示，將採用「創新」的罷工時間表，由4月起基本上<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>每隔三日罷工連續兩日</strong></span></span>，直到今年6月28日為止，連同周四合計的罷工日子為37日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2hrijM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2hrijM2.jpg&h=86eeaecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7a52a2ff7fdddb66a16b472adcaa5655b6e71de3","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70e7bb997198fe8c8505059c246a14dc75163406","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a08acae39e9c13f67dd25610fff68ac1e7c5406e","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da928068ce8de9a38afc74272f4bf9438cda4c78","tid":1383431,"uid":292366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"577a95ce3f9e286c71052865cc583c6717375a2a","tid":1383431,"uid":68822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=c298983b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/C52Yh8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC52Yh8p.png&h=abd1676d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/LsES61O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsES61O.png&h=05c3ec63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/atvOG1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatvOG1X.jpg&h=d71d8eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"003bd7eb6415336a552bce54ad986c9636b2ef32","tid":1383431,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42457c1d0a602d7304b96d70fc5e2a2f3b9712b8","tid":1383431,"uid":269963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37c9c81d4f18753c55859afab801a29e3d0ad3a7","tid":1383431,"uid":289262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:50:37.000Z","msg":"我要罷工<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"fb4748b533c60060ca548f47876e22e09245a35a","tid":1383431,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:51:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ea0015e4a96d92f5437b314b90efeec17864dcc","tid":1383431,"uid":246741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"法國罷工schedule真係無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5177b86bb6499bf6dad86b5c89988546ce409099","tid":1383431,"uid":167973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"大家早啲瞓<br />\n聽朝730呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48234dc3b4cbcc632a8afb78ca4cc5b81a94aceb","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"9e88e6381a987bbbd8b62b2f7ba8910fe4041a49","tid":1383431,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:27:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">推啊 車長需要我地配合！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b81c15e5db5682e7a393f7b5a410e00159531366","tid":1383431,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"好名"},{"pid":"b08cc06c132b76cf47f88de29abbae0bed1cef37","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"5b69f391ad110bb065b96508c8d642513385c723","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b08cc06c132b76cf47f88de29abbae0bed1cef37","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"推下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"屌，講錯<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"c17f07f6841e4779de7c827ff9ca3afc4ed28274","tid":1383431,"uid":115264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f5b3aaad3b638c375b4a21d522c41e784ab3475","tid":1383431,"uid":64938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:05:18.000Z","msg":"[香城online]傳令兵的技巧和心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d45d9fa834e0f88e3defd81bce3f10430f11232a","tid":1383431,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:40:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37fd21fd32d4de5360e835a3c355451cc68a05f9","tid":1383431,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:41:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3e1271d920c1c6bdf2199b823dc5ff69d3b7c1b","tid":1383431,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:49:05.000Z","msg":"有冇禁制組 病人可以pm @zisusername<br />\n病人好簡單，你比人撞到你突然腰痛要訓係地下郁唔到，其他人會黎幫你手企隔離<br />\n<br />\n7月30不合作運動 及 8月5罷工行動整合<br />\n<br />\n7月30日港鐵不合作運動之詳情<br />\n<br />\n公海TG Channel：@sitmtr<br />\n公海TG Group：@mstopthem<br />\n<br />\n日期：7月30日<br />\n時間：07:30<br />\n地點：調景嶺地鐵站上車<br />\n人數：自己及現實朋友一位，若多於兩人請扮唔識（切勿ONLINE組隊）<br />\n隨身物件：行李箱、公事包、背包等（切勿攜帶任何可疑或危險物品）<br />\n衣著：普通上班／上學服飾（冇DRESS CODE，切勿過份張揚）<br />\n<br />\n（Ａ）行動目標<br />\n癱瘓港鐵及交通，以致罷工罷課罷市，迫使政府回應訴求。<br />\n<br />\n（Ｂ）行動內容<br />\n齊齊搭港鐵，如果見到有病人病倒，作為熱心市民，請拉手掣，等待盡責嘅港鐵職員提供協助，並保護好病人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（１）其他行為<br />\n切勿做其他激烈或犯法行為，呢個活動係俾和理非／承受唔到風險嘅人出一分力參與爭取，一切安全至上。請記住，行動只係守法搭地鐵，車箱內如果有人絆倒／有病人暈倒，請各位熱心市民提供協助並保護傷者／病人，例如：月台緊急制／車頭車尾逃生門，容後再討論或視乎現場人數再跟隨Admin指示。<br />\n<br />\n「車長很怕斷了繩索的逃生門，怕得會請病假」 - 港鐵車長<br />\n<br />\n（２）點解搞地鐵，會喪失民意喎<br />\n有人話要有政治智慧，唔好搞地鐵，搞到普通市民冇得返工返學。但其實你做任何嘢，衝擊立法會，靜坐，遊行，甚至乜都唔做，都可以有唔同嘅人怪罪於你。各有各做，無需刻意爭取同情或體諒，加上輿論形勢控制唔到。好多野都會失民心，但係做左就有機會，唔做就一定冇<br />\n<br />\n（３）自發／各自搞得唔得？<br />\n得，但唔建議。因為唔會有明顯效果，6月14日同7月25日係好例子，唔夠人做冇人保護，各有各做只會係一盤散沙。不如團結啲，安全地集體行動，大家保護大家，拖延嘅時間可以更長。<br />\n<br />\n（４）喺其他站／喺其他時間搞得唔得？<br />\n之後有可能會喺其他站搞，但先統一7月30日喺調景嶺上車。揀07:30係因為上班時間，返工嘅一定係呢啲時間返，其他時間作用同影響唔大，下班時間唔好搞。所以07:30，真係真係唔好遲到。<br />\n<br />\n（５）如遭拘捕／截查／罰款<br />\n冇做壞事光明正大唔洗驚，唔好被兇到，最緊要清楚自己權利。以防萬一請事先記低律師電話，其他需知可以喺其他地方搵到，呢到就唔詳述。另外可嘗試使用國語或英文同警察／港鐵職員交流對答，香港係國際都會嚟。大家良好市民，盡量唔好發生衝突，記得要有禮貌，但如果見到有其他良好市民被粗暴對待或恐嚇，請挺身而出幫幫手，保護好大家。如果有市民真係不幸被捕／罰款，請搵方法喺群組入面或同Admin講聲，事後記得拎口供紙同報平安。<br />\n<br />\n我冇嘢講，我要去醫院，我要見律師，我唔解鎖電話，我唔簽任何文件。<br />\n<br />\n（６）口罩／帽／服飾<br />\n普通返工咁著就可以。口罩／帽自己決定，冇需要刻意掩飾身份惹人懷疑，冇DRESS CODE，切勿過份張揚。<br />\n<br />\n（７）互相保護<br />\n全程盡量望實手機同打吓字，請小心螢幕亮度同隔離嘅人。另外亦要留意身邊情況，如有其他市民需要協助，請作出支援，保護大家之餘亦要保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n（８）個群組有鬼<br />\n個群組係一定會有鬼／狗，避唔到。唔需要捉鬼，唔駛理佢，Admin見到自然會踢。當日行動期間一定會有記者同狗，一切跟現場指示應變。如果現場發現唔夠人Admin亦會有可能叫散水，安全至上，冇人想有人出事。記住你只係搭地鐵返工返學，冇犯任何法例，唔需要驚。另外，請記者朋友手下留情，呢種時勢請盡量唔好影人樣。<br />\n<br />\n（９）地面交通<br />\n死火燈為記認，全港大塞車，歡迎有車市民配合。<br />\n<br />\n（１０）失敗咁多次仲要搞？<br />\n失敗原因係因為每一次都唔夠人，你試諗下你會唔會可以承受成車都望住你嘅目光自己去頂門？只要成功到呢一次，大家知點玩就好容易可以發起第二次，第三次。<br />\n<br />\n（１１）總結<br />\n最後，有人可能會好興奮同覺得好好玩，有好多意見同建議，但有啲人可能根本唔會去現場，所以請小心一切帶風向言論。選擇參與嘅話請先清楚明白目的同理念，唔認同呢種做法嘅亦請你離開，各有各做。如有疑問，請重睇行動內容及本說明書或直接聯絡Admin。任何無關討論／無關消息／帶風向／鼓吹犯法或送頭行為／唔睇哂詳程就問問題／講阻住人返工／講喪失民意／講唔好塞地鐵嘅，全部一律即踢，要講自己返連登或者其他群組講。呢到只係一眾市民守法搭觀塘線返工返學，去感受地鐵世界頂級嘅服務質素。完。<br />\n<br />\n公海TG Channel：@sitmtr<br />\n公海TG Group：@mstopthem<br />\n<br />\n宜家呢個時勢已經係最佳時機去升級<br />\n&ldquo;It&rsquo;s now or never.＂<br />\n<br />\n8月5日7區集會及全港大三罷之詳情<br />\n<br />\n公海tg channel：@saveinghk<br />\n公海tg grp：@saveinghkgrp"},{"pid":"b46892eb17ba8d15ea0f1763bcee4cc3d3503649","tid":1383431,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b69f391ad110bb065b96508c8d642513385c723","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b08cc06c132b76cf47f88de29abbae0bed1cef37","tid":1383431,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"推下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"屌，講錯<br />\n我冇野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:50:49.000Z","msg":"倒不如&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=7467f6e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"956127059473376f3d48b24e305a7417d9cfba1f","tid":1383431,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96874f0e3184a5513f0e47e3324085b211bd6b0","tid":1383431,"uid":266879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:10:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}